Check fluid level in your reservoir. Then have someone pump the brakes
repeatedly while you crawl around underneath looking for leaks.

I can't say I've ever had a hard line break on any car. Not
impossible, of course. But for me it's always been the soft hoses from
the hard lines to the wheels.

